If 
\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\left|a_{n}\right|$
\end_inset

 converges, then the series 
\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}a_{n}$
\end_inset

 converges.
\end_layout

