: A power series is a series of the form 
\begin_inset Formula $\sum c_{n}x^{n}=ùëê_{0}+ùëê_{1}ùë•+ùëê_{2}ùë•^{2}+ùëê_{3}ùë•^{3}‚Ä¶$
\end_inset

where 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

