 & =f\left(0\right)+\frac{f'\left(0\right)}{1!}+\frac{f''\left(0\right)}{2!}x^{2}+\frac{f'''\left(0\right)}{3!}x^{3}+...
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
is called the 
\series bold
Maclaurin Series.
